Entity Rellenador
Architecture Rellenador_Arquitectura
Enginer B0vE
Description Un sencillo código de ejemplo

Binary c0, c1, c2, c3, salida
Binary[1,0] s
Integer[0,3] control

control = (integer) s

If control = 0 then salida = c0
else if control = 1 then salida = c1
else if control = 2 then salida = c2
else salida = c3

